Date: Sat, 18 Apr 2026 17:12:16 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 1/6] chore(ux): add Puppeteer-based UX exploration runner

Adds tools/ux/ with a click-through runner that logs in, walks every
top tab, exercises detail tabs, captures full-page screenshots at
desktop + mobile viewports, and writes report.json + summary.md
grouped by severity. Used to drive the auto-patch loop in
docs/tasks/ux-exploration.md.
