- Spawn a fresh Chrome per viewport so localStorage isolation no longer
  depends on createBrowserContext semantics that vary across
  puppeteer-core builds.
- Wait for React to leave its 'Loading...' splash before probing for
  the login form; otherwise a slow /auth/status round-trip looks
  identical to a fail-open render of the dashboard.
- Probe for the sign-in card after every goto and report a critical
  'auth-fail-open' issue when the dashboard renders without a token.
- Dedupe issues by (severity, view, message) so 5s polling no longer
  floods the report with identical 401 lines.
- Clear localStorage between flows and respect an expectAuth flag so
  401 noise during deliberate token-clear / logout windows is not
  counted as a regression.
